data.description: This beautiful property offers the perfect blend of spaciousness and natural beauty. Situated on a generous acre lot, this well-maintained home boasts four bedrooms and three-and-a-half bathrooms. Step outside onto the two decks and take in the tranquility of your wooded backyard, providing privacy and a lovely backdrop for outdoor activities and relaxation. The ample space is perfect for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Convenience is key, with a half bathroom situated on the main level for guests' use and a full basement offering extra living and storage space. The attached garage provides shelter for your vehicles and additional storage, ensuring maximum functionality. Located on the southeast side of Cedar Rapids, this home offers a peaceful suburban setting while still being within easy reach of amenities, schools, and parks. 1 year warranty comes with purchase from APW
